member.name: AUTOCOMPLETELISTOPTIONS
member.summary: Specifies which objects are enumerated for autocompletion lists.

member.name: AUTOCOMPLETELISTOPTIONS.ACLO_CURRENTDIR
member.summary: Only the current directory should be enumerated.

member.name: AUTOCOMPLETELISTOPTIONS.ACLO_DESKTOP
member.summary: Only the Desktop Folder should be enumerated.

member.name: AUTOCOMPLETELISTOPTIONS.ACLO_FAVORITES
member.summary: Only the Favorites Folder should be enumerated.

member.name: AUTOCOMPLETELISTOPTIONS.ACLO_FILESYSONLY
member.summary: Only the file system should be enumerated.

member.name: AUTOCOMPLETELISTOPTIONS.ACLO_FILESYSDIRS
member.summary: Internet Explorer 6 or greater: The file system dirs, UNC shares, and UNC servers should be enumerated.

member.name: AUTOCOMPLETELISTOPTIONS.ACLO_VIRTUALNAMESPACE
member.summary: Windows Internet Explorer 7 or greater: The virtual namespace should be enumerated.
